<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Volunteer Appreciation</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 5px;
        box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      h1 {
        color: #333333;
      }
      p {
        color: #777777;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #55a5ff;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Thank You, Volunteers!</h1>
      <p>Dear <%= volunteerName %>,</p>
      <p><%= body %></p>
      <p>
        Thank you for being a part of the <%= projectName %> project. Your dedication and hard work are greatly
        appreciated!
      </p>
      <p>
        If you have any questions or need further information, please don't hesitate to reach out to us. We value your
        contribution and look forward to achieving great success together.
      </p>
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p>The <%= projectName %> Team</p>
      <p>
        <a class="button" href="https://www.example.com">Visit The Libera Website</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
